---
import Locations from '@/components/Locations.astro'
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Home - Designo">
  <main class="md:px-10 lg:px-[165px] overlay-img">
    <section
      class="md:rounded-[15px] md:mb-[120px] lg:mb-40 md:overflow-hidden bg-peach-500 lg:flex bg-[url(/assets/company/mobile/bg-pattern-hero-about-mobile.svg)] md:bg-circle-pattern bg-[position:top_180px_right] md:bg-[position:top_-100px_left_-100px] lg:bg-[position:top_-160px_left] bg-no-repeat"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-[url(/assets/company/mobile/image-about-hero.jpg)] lg:order-2 md:bg-[url(/assets/company/tablet/image-about-hero.jpg)] lg:bg-[url(/assets/company/desktop/image-about-hero.jpg)] bg-cover bg-no-repeat w-full h-80 lg:h-[480px] xl:min-w-[476px]"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="py-20 md:py-16 px-6 xl:pl-24 lg:w-full md:px-14 lg:py-0 lg:justify-center flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start gap-6 md:gap-8 text-white"
      >
        <h1 class="text-[32px] leading-9 md:text-5xl font-medium">About Us</h1>
        <p class="text-center lg:text-left xl:max-w-md">
          Founded in 2010, we are a creative agency that produces lasting
          results for our clients. We’ve partnered with many startups,
          corporations, and nonprofits alike to craft designs that make real
          impact. We’re always looking forward to creating brands, products, and
          digital experiences that connect with our clients’ audiences.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="md:rounded-[15px] lg:flex md:overflow-hidden bg-[#fdf3f0] bg-[url(/assets/company/bg-pattern-sections.svg)] bg-[position:bottom_left] md:bg-[position:bottom_45px_left_100px] lg:bg-[position:bottom_right_-50px] bg-no-repeat"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-[url(/assets/company/mobile/image-world-class-talent.jpg)] md:bg-[url(/assets/company/tablet/image-world-class-talent.jpg)] lg:bg-[url(/assets/company/desktop/image-world-class-talent.jpg)] bg-cover bg-no-repeat w-full h-80 lg:h-[640px] xl:min-w-[476px]"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="py-20 px-6 md:px-14 md:py-16 xl:pl-24 flex lg:w-full flex-col items-center lg:items-start lg:justify-center gap-6"
      >
        <h2
          class="text-orange-500 text-[32px] md:text-[40px] md:leading-[48px] leading-9 font-medium"
        >
          World-class talent
        </h2>
        <p class="text-center lg:text-left xl:max-w-md">
          We are a crew of strategists, problem-solvers, and technologists.
          Every design is thoughtfully crafted from concept to launch, ensuring
          success in its given market. We are constantly updating our skills in
          a myriad of platforms.
          <br />
          <br />
          Our team is multi-disciplinary and we are not merely interested in form
          — content and meaning are just as important. We give great importance to
          craftsmanship, service, and prompt delivery. Clients have always been impressed
          with our high-quality outcomes that encapsulates their brand’s story and
          mission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Locations />

    <section
      class="md:rounded-[15px] md:overflow-hidden mb-[120px] lg:mb-40 lg:flex bg-[#fdf3f0] bg-[url(/assets/company/bg-pattern-sections.svg)] bg-[position:bottom_left] md:bg-[position:bottom_45px_left_100px] lg:bg-[position:bottom_left] bg-no-repeat"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-[url(/assets/company/mobile/image-real-deal.jpg)] lg:order-2 md:bg-[url(/assets/company/tablet/image-real-deal.jpg)] lg:bg-[url(/assets/company/desktop/image-real-deal.jpg)] bg-cover bg-no-repeat w-full h-80 lg:h-[640px] xl:min-w-[476px]"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="py-20 px-6 lg:w-full md:px-14 md:py-16 xl:pl-24 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start lg:justify-center gap-6"
      >
        <h2 class="text-orange-500 text-[32px] leading-9 font-medium">
          The real deal
        </h2>
        <p class="text-center lg:text-left xl:max-w-md">
          As strategic partners in our clients’ businesses, we are ready to take
          on any challenge as our own. Solving real problems require empathy and
          collaboration, and we strive to bring a fresh perspective to every
          opportunity. We make design and technology more accessible and give
          you tools to measure success.
          <br />
          <br />
          We are visual storytellers in appealing and captivating ways. By combining
          business and marketing strategies, we inspire audiences to take action
          and drive real results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style scoped>
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .overlay-img {
      background-image: url(/assets/shared/bg-pattern-leaf.svg),
        url(/assets/shared/bg-pattern-leaf.svg);
      background-repeat: no-repeat, no-repeat;
      background-position: top 200px left, bottom 400px right -300px;
    }
  }
</style>
